## Input

```css
div {
  // Plain `(` branch: regular function heads inside `url(...)` should still
  // parse as modifier functions even when recovery is needed.
  plain-branch-missing-close: url(join-url("..", "image.png");

  // UrlBody branch: malformed interpolation inside the function head should
  // still preserve the interpolated-function shape for recovery.
  interpolated-start-missing-curly: url(#{name(bar));
  interpolated-mid-broken-interpolation: url(foo#{1 + }(bar));
  interpolated-mid-missing-curly: url(foo#{1 + 1(bar));
}

```


